All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

[1.0.0] - 2026-04-17
Added

Initial release of the SpaceX Falcon 9 Landing Prediction system.

Data ingestion scripts for SpaceX API and web scraped Wikipedia data.

Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) notebooks with Seaborn and Matplotlib.

Interactive launch site maps using Folium.

Plotly Dash dashboard for real-time payload and site filtering.

Machine Learning pipeline comparing Logistic Regression, SVM, Decision Tree, and KNN.

Hyperparameter tuning using GridSearchCV.
